  m_text: 'In premonition your goal is to defeat all the evil skeletons in as little
    time possible and suffering as little damage.


    Score = # Turns + # Damage


    The
    lower the score the better.


    Even thought you can suffer damage, you are
    invincible and cannot die. The only way to "lose" is to get stuck between dead
    skeletons.'
