  m_text: 'You can move when tiles around you start pulsating. Left-click on a tile
    to move there.


    You can attack when an enemie''s head is pulsating red.
    Before attacking choose the amount of energy spent by clicking W and S to increase
    or decrease the amount. Click on an enemy to attack them.


    Use the scroll
    wheel to zoom in and out. Hold right-click and drag to change the angle of the
    camera.'
